Description: PDF to Markdown converter powered by local Ollama vision models
 mdify converts PDF documents into clean Markdown using a local
 Ollama vision-language model (Qwen2.5-VL). Every page is rendered
 as an image and fed to the VLM for precise OCR — tables, diagrams,
 pinouts, and technical drawings are all captured as structured Markdown.
 .
 Features:
  - Fully local: no cloud APIs, no data leaves your machine
  - Automatic Ollama setup and model management
  - High-fidelity OCR for tables and technical drawings
  - Batch processing with parallel workers
  - Programmatic Python API
